name: Soul Dogs City Bones
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Super-high quality, retro-inspired 3D Soul Dogs NFTs living in Soul Dogs city. Put your dogs to work by staking and earn $BONES. Use bones to upgrade your NFTs, play games, and purchase other items in the Soul Dogs City Metaverse.
